title: Cloudflare Warp
extract: Cloudflare Warp. Cloudflare Warp is a security-conscious tool for exposing web applications without needing to expose the server they run on. ... Traffic can never hit your origin directly because it can never find it, your origin isn't on the internet, it's only there if you go through Cloudflare, via Warp.Sep 28, 2017
